    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"You wanna go bro?\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefits-strong-\"><strong>Benefits</strong></h5><p>You aren't afraid to take cheap shots. Twice per short rest, when you roll initative, you can make a melee attack as a free action against a creature within your weapon's range.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative</strong></h5><p>When you take your trick shot you leave yourself wide open to attack. When you would use the benefit of this trait your AC is lowered by 2 until the beginning of your first turn.</p>",
